OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with a blustery breeze,
OL,6,Fstrong across the Pennines. Dry start
OL,7,Ffor many, but some light rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle possible, mainly in the west.
OL,9,FRain spreading to most parts through
OL,10,Fthe morning, occasionally heavy,
OL,11,Fbefore easing later in the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny rain or drizzle soon
OL,14,Feasing, with a few clearer spells
OL,15,Fpossible in the north. Otherwise
OL,16,Fstaying rather cloudy, with hill fog
OL,17,Facross the southern Pennines. Winds
OL,18,Fbecoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
