OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloud thinning and breaking,
OL,6,Fand perhaps the odd sunny spell
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Although some thicker
OL,8,Fcloud could allow for a few spots of
OL,9,Frain or drizzle, mainly in the south.
OL,10,FMild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fwith rain Saturday morning, clearing
OL,14,Fto brighter spells later, and
OL,15,Fovernight frost. Winds strengthening
OL,16,FSunday and Monday, with some rain
OL,17,Fspreading east, but also drier and
OL,18,Fbrighter intervals. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
